channel.title: [PI] Models
channel.description:
I add the models into the Raw folder. I add the ints into the ItemDef.java .. I go on the server and type in add model, a box pops up, and I enter the model #. It says Unable to find model. #####
Can someone please help me over teamviewer or just tell me what to do? I've spent over 2 hours trying to do it now.
EDIT3: FIXED! I had to enable pre-loading and increase the modelindex to 1!
